name: Bobby Jack’s Game Progress
abstract: This is a list of video games and how much progress I’ve made with them
words:
this is simply an attempt to catalogue my game completion across various titles, mainly on switch.
    games are marked as
inished (which more or less means ‘seen credits’) or

ompleted (typically meaning all available % achieved).
    i’ve also included a small explanation, where it can clarify progress, and screenshots offering ‘proof’.
